<title>GERMANY: Bayer details H1 figures by region.</title>
<headline>Bayer details H1 figures by region.</headline>
<dateline>LEVERKUSEN, Germany 1997-08-19</dateline>
<text>
<p>Six months to end June</p>
<p>(in millions of marks unless stated)</p>
<p>    Group sales				  27,418  vs 24,79</p>
<p>Sales by market</p>
<p>     Europe					13,418  vs 12,747</p>
<p>     North America			     7,177   vs 6,066</p>
<p>     Latin America			     1,996   vs 1,636</p>
<p>     Asia/Africa/Australia		   4,827   vs 4,348</p>
<p>Sales by point of origin</p>
<p>     Europe					15,384  vs 14,548</p>
<p>     North America			     7,243   vs 6,080</p>
<p>     Latin America			     1,685   vs 1,322</p>
<p>     Asia/Africa/Australia		   3,106   vs 2,841</p>
<p>    Operating result			   2,959   vs 2,783</p>
<p>By region</p>
<p>     Europe					2,120   vs 1,915</p>
<p>     North America			     540     vs 569</p>
<p>     Latin America			     109     vs 115</p>
<p>     Asia/Africa/Australia		   190     vs 184</p>
<p>    Return on sales			    10.8%   vs 11.2%</p>
<p>By region</p>
<p>     Europe					13.8%   vs 13.2%</p>
<p>     North America			     7.5%    vs 9.3%</p>
<p>     Latin America			     6.5%    vs 8.8%</p>
<p>     Asia/Africa/Australia		   6.1%    vs 6.5%</p>
<p>NOTE - Full name of the German chemical group is Bayer AG.</p>
<p>-- Frankfurt Newsroom +49 69 756525</p>
